These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, polish, argentine
1. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
2. the argentine is between the brazilian and the pakistani##2
3. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | argentine | pakistani | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, tomato, lime, radish
1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating radish##1
2. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | tomato | pepper | radish | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, comedy, fantasy, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
2. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | western | fantasy | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is volleyball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | sailing | cycling | swimming | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
