2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | skiing | ice-hockey | cricket | parkour |

